Choose from this set of possible answers [ convīvae colloquuntur dē fugā Mēdī et dē poenīs servōrum, hospitēs interrogat dē rēbus urbānīs, ... quia ipse paucās epistulās scrībit, Mēdum vīdit in viā Latīnā, Orontēs fābulam nārrat dē Midā rēge, Iūlius dē suō Mēdō servō loquī māvult, Midās omnia manū tangendō in aurum mūtāre poterat, hoc mūnus illī dederat Bacchus, rēx miser fuit quod cibus eius in aurum mūtābātur, Bacchus eī suāsit ut in quōdam flūmine lavārētur, color aquae aureus factus est, Iūlius nārrat ‘Mēdum cum pecūniā dominī aufūgisse, Iūlius dīcit ‘omnēs servōs suōs īnfīdōs esse praeter ūnum’] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-babbage-001' where ANSWER in [ 'convīvae colloquuntur dē fugā Mēdī et dē poenīs servōrum', 'hospitēs interrogat dē rēbus urbānīs', '... quia ipse paucās epistulās scrībit', 'Mēdum vīdit in viā Latīnā', 'Orontēs fābulam nārrat dē Midā rēge', 'Iūlius dē suō Mēdō servō loquī māvult', 'Midās omnia manū tangendō in aurum mūtāre poterat', 'hoc mūnus illī dederat Bacchus', 'rēx miser fuit quod cibus eius in aurum mūtābātur', 'Bacchus eī suāsit ut in quōdam flūmine lavārētur', 'color aquae aureus factus est', 'Iūlius nārrat ‘Mēdum cum pecūniā dominī aufūgisse'', 'Iūlius dīcit ‘omnēs servōs suōs īnfīdōs esse praeter ūnum’']
codes.answer: Iūlius dīcit ‘omnēs servōs suōs īnfīdōs esse praeter ūnum’
